These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
City: london, venice
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| City        | london   | venice   |
| Transport   | scooter | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, mango
1. the person eating watermelon is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice   |
| Food      | mango | watermelon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
