There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up
1. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
2. the person eating peach is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | peach | cabbage |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | 7up     |

